entries.npc_breech_1: I knew they'd figure it out eventually.
entries.otherescort_1: I'm not the one you seek.
entries.npc_failure_1: That's a bit of a disappointment. I'll need to find another way to handle this matter.
entries.npc_noloc_1: We have someone keeping an eye on her. He'll contact me when she leaves town. See me in a little while.
entries.npc_work_1: I'd hate for that informant to pass on more information. Were you going to finish this mission soon?
entries.npc_reward_1: You have served Black Sun well.
entries.npc_backtowork_1: I've told you all I can. Are you going to take care of this?
entries.npc_4_1: A Twi'lek dancer named Kalar'naa. She's the common link to several information leaks that have troubled us recently. She leaves town to meet her contact every few days. Will you see to it that she doesn't do that again?
entries.npc_3_1: Then I suppose we have no business to conduct with one another.
entries.npc_2_1: Good. It would be best if something happened to her after she leaves town. We'd rather this problem disappeared quietly.
entries.npc_1_1: You were wise to seek me out -- Black Sun is a force to be reckoned with on this world. Are you looking for work? I have a job that's perfect for a freelancer such as yourself. The Lady Hutt has planted an agent in our midst. We need this agent removed. Will you do the removal?
entries.npc_reset: Check back and see me when you're a little tougher. I'll still have a job for you.
entries.cantwork: You already have a job. When it's finished, see me.
entries.next: I don't have any more work for you right now. I'll keep you in mind when something else comes up.
